                    maṟ·ṟ’ itaṉai
                    <lb n="6r5=82" break="no"/>k· kāt·tāraṉ· malar-aṭi Eṉ· muṭi mēlaṉa E		
                    <lb n="6r6=83" break="no"/>ṉ·ṟu koṟ·ṟavaṉē-y· paṇitt-aruḷi-t· teṟṟ’ eṉa	
                    <pb n="6v"/><lb n="6v1=84"/><hi rend="grantha">tāmra-śāsana</hi>ñ· cey·vit·tāṉ· <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g>        
